{"title":"Ubuntu16-04-LTS：anaconda3安装","slug":"ubuntu16_04_LTS_anaconda3安装","date":"2022-11-23T21:00:02.000Z","updated":"2023-11-24T15:25:15.590Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/ubuntu16_04_LTS_anaconda3安装.json","excerpt":null,"covers":["https://i.loli.net/2021/05/16/9curYTMUWmveogb.png","https://i.loli.net/2021/05/16/JU2iRojd3vH4fsY.png","https://i.loli.net/2021/05/16/iVDa14zUNREPYKs.png","https://i.loli.net/2021/05/16/DBj5P8VMTzgYu2s.png"],"content":"<h1 id=\"1-下载清华源镜像文件\"><a href=\"#1-下载清华源镜像文件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. 下载清华源镜像文件\"></a>1. 下载清华源镜像文件</h1><p>网址：<a href=\"https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/anaconda/archive/\">https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/anaconda/archive/</a></p>\n<p>版本：建议安装Anaconda3-5.2.0-Linux-x86_64.sh</p>\n<h1 id=\"2-进入下载目录执行以下命令进行安装\"><a href=\"#2-进入下载目录执行以下命令进行安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2. 进入下载目录执行以下命令进行安装\"></a>2. 进入下载目录执行以下命令进行安装</h1><figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">bash Anaconda3<span class=\"number\">-5.2</span><span class=\"number\">.0</span>-Linux-x86_64.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/05/16/9curYTMUWmveogb.png\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>一路按回车至底部，出现提示：是否接受安装协议时：回复yes:</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/05/16/JU2iRojd3vH4fsY.png\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>默认的路径为&#x2F;home&#x2F;username&#x2F;anaconda3，默认的话直接按ENTER即可，等待安装过程完成即可。</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/05/16/iVDa14zUNREPYKs.png\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>询问是否将Anaconda3加入到环境变量中，选：yes</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/05/16/DBj5P8VMTzgYu2s.png\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>默认的话直接按ENTER即可，等待安装过程完成即可。</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"3-检查是否安装成功\"><a href=\"#3-检查是否安装成功\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3.检查是否安装成功\"></a>3.检查是否安装成功</h1><p>  使用以下命令可以查看已经存在的conda虚拟环境</p>\n  <figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">conda env list</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>  使用以下命令可以查看conda的路径是否添加成功</p>\n  <figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo gedit ~/.bashrc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>  使其立即生效，在终端执行：</p>\n  <figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">source ~/.bashrc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>  <strong>4.进入任意一个创建的虚拟环境里面检查python</strong></p>\n<p>  在虚拟环境中输入以下命令：</p>\n  <figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">python</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>  会出现类似以下含有anaconda的字样：</p>\n  <figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Python <span class=\"number\">3.6</span><span class=\"number\">.5</span> |Anaconda, Inc.| (<span class=\"keyword\">default</span>, Apr <span class=\"number\">29</span> <span class=\"number\">2018</span>, <span class=\"number\">16</span>:<span class=\"number\">14</span>:<span class=\"number\">56</span>) </span><br><span class=\"line\">[GCC <span class=\"number\">7.2</span><span class=\"number\">.0</span>] on linux</span><br><span class=\"line\">Type <span class=\"string\">&quot;help&quot;</span>, <span class=\"string\">&quot;copyright&quot;</span>, <span class=\"string\">&quot;credits&quot;</span> <span class=\"keyword\">or</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;license&quot;</span> <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> more information.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>  如果没有出现以下字样，说明系统的python版本需要指定，使用以下命令：</p>\n  <figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo gedit ~/.bashrc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>  在bashrc中添加一行：</p>\n  <figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">alias python=python3</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>  (注意这里的python3是和安装的anaconda3对应的默认pyrhon对应的，可以在conda虚拟环境中的base环境中查看对应的python版本)</p>\n<p>  然后激活bashrc</p>\n  <figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">source</span> ~/.bashrc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>  这样就可以使用conda创建的虚拟环境对应的python。</p>\n<script type=\"text&#x2F;javascript\" src=\"https://unpkg.com/kity@2.0.4/dist/kity.min.js\"></script><script type=\"text&#x2F;javascript\" src=\"https://unpkg.com/kityminder-core@1.4.50/dist/kityminder.core.min.js\"></script><script defer=\"true\" type=\"text&#x2F;javascript\" src=\"https://unpkg.com/hexo-simple-mindmap@0.8.0/dist/mindmap.min.js\"></script><link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text&#x2F;css\" href=\"https://unpkg.com/hexo-simple-mindmap@0.8.0/dist/mindmap.min.css\">","more":"<h1 id=\"1-下载清华源镜像文件\"><a href=\"#1-下载清华源镜像文件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. 下载清华源镜像文件\"></a>1. 下载清华源镜像文件</h1><p>网址：<a href=\"https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/anaconda/archive/\">https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/anaconda/archive/</a></p>\n<p>版本：建议安装Anaconda3-5.2.0-Linux-x86_64.sh</p>\n<h1 id=\"2-进入下载目录执行以下命令进行安装\"><a href=\"#2-进入下载目录执行以下命令进行安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2. 进入下载目录执行以下命令进行安装\"></a>2. 进入下载目录执行以下命令进行安装</h1><figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">bash Anaconda3<span class=\